200
00:16:05,451 --> 00:16:07,186
Mayday!

201
00:16:10,189 --> 00:16:11,758
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GROANS)</font></b>

202
00:16:12,558 --> 00:16:13,727
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(COUGHS)</font></b>

203
00:16:15,095 --> 00:16:16,697
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(VOMITING)</font></b>

204
00:16:18,865 --> 00:16:20,332
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(COUGHING)</font></b>

205
00:16:22,035 --> 00:16:23,770
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font></b>

206
00:16:24,637 --> 00:16:26,205
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CRYING)</font></b>

207
00:16:33,780 --> 00:16:35,681
Where are you?

208
00:16:42,923 --> 00:16:44,557
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CONTINUES CRYING)</font></b>

209
00:17:07,948 --> 00:17:09,080
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI GRUNTS)</font></b>

210
00:17:09,082 --> 00:17:10,784
- Where are you taking me?
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font></b>

211
00:17:18,759 --> 00:17:20,526
This is unreal. <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GIGGLES)</font></b>

212
00:17:25,698 --> 00:17:27,664
Wow.

213
00:17:27,666 --> 00:17:29,633
Ooh, you're not gonna jump,
are you?

214
00:17:29,635 --> 00:17:32,003
No, of course I'm not.

215
00:17:32,005 --> 00:17:34,040
- Shut up.
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI LAUGHS)</font></b>

216
