650
00:46:46,525 --> 00:46:49,024
<i>Dad, if he's around.</i>

651
00:46:49,026 --> 00:46:51,161
<i>I'll see you soon.
I love you so much.</i>

652
00:46:52,931 --> 00:46:54,831
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GROANS)</font></b> That's it.

653
00:46:54,833 --> 00:46:56,868
