00:49:25,649 --> 00:49:28,084
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font></b>
- Wait a second...

706
00:49:28,086 --> 00:49:29,551
- Aw.
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(RICHARD LAUGHING)</font></b>

