00:50:43,228 --> 00:50:44,961
Oi, no, no, no.
We need to ration now.

728
00:50:44,963 --> 00:50:46,428
Okay, you wanna
starve to death?

729
00:50:46,430 --> 00:50:47,930
You wanna be a victim,
be my guest.

730
00:50:47,932 --> 00:50:49,098
You make it sound like
it's a choice.

731
00:50:49,100 --> 00:50:51,033
- It is a choice, Tam.
- It's not a choice!

732
00:50:51,035 --> 00:50:53,504
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(METAL CREAKING)</font></b>
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI SIGHS)</font></b>

733
00:50:54,304 --> 00:50:56,540
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CREAKING CONTINUES)</font></b>
