00:54:22,080 --> 00:54:23,714
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font></b>

758
00:54:39,130 --> 00:54:41,230
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">RICHARD:</font></b> Is everything okay
down there?

759
00:54:41,232 --> 00:54:42,367
Yeah.

760
00:54:47,338 --> 00:54:49,173
