00:56:50,294 --> 00:56:51,695
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font></b>

793
00:57:03,474 --> 00:57:06,007
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font></b> I can't do it.

