795
00:57:08,412 --> 00:57:09,913
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI GRUNTING)</font></b>

796
00:57:11,114 --> 00:57:12,450
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">RICHARD:</font></b> It's okay.

797
00:57:17,321 --> 00:57:19,590
I can't do it. <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GASPING)</font></b>

798
00:57:23,161 --> 00:57:24,362
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(SHUSHING)</font></b>

799
00:57:47,017 --> 00:57:48,852
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font></b>

