00:58:10,974 --> 00:58:12,376
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(LAUGHS)</font></b>

802
00:58:17,682 --> 00:58:19,749
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">TAMI:</font></b> What you got
