857
01:02:37,741 --> 01:02:39,042
Uh...

858
01:02:39,976 --> 01:02:41,409
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font></b>

859
01:02:41,411 --> 01:02:43,946
"So it's true
