868
01:03:17,313 --> 01:03:18,448
I love you.

869
01:03:19,550 --> 01:03:21,382
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">TAMI:</font></b> Mmm-hmm...

870
01:03:21,384 --> 01:03:24,387
