01:05:09,492 --> 01:05:11,327
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(WHIMPERING)</font></b>

896
01:05:13,162 --> 01:05:14,765
No, no, no...

897
01:05:16,332 --> 01:05:20,102
How could you not see us?
We're right here!

898
01:05:20,104 --> 01:05:21,739
We're right here!

899
01:05:24,240 --> 01:05:25,807
Where did you go?

900
01:05:25,809 --> 01:05:27,310
