904
01:05:38,154 --> 01:05:40,789
Oh, my God,
we're gonna die out here!

905
01:05:40,791 --> 01:05:42,760
We're gonna die out here!

906
01:05:45,561 --> 01:05:46,730
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">RICHARD:</font></b> We might.

907
01:05:47,965 --> 01:05:50,366
