to say that!

908
01:05:51,200 --> 01:05:52,466
You'd rather I lied to you?

909
01:05:52,468 --> 01:05:54,468
Yes, please lie to me.

910
01:05:54,470 --> 01:05:57,405
Just tell me
it's gonna be okay.

911
01:05:57,407 --> 01:05:59,275
