913
01:06:02,880 --> 01:06:04,380
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(RICHARD GROANS)</font></b>

914
01:06:08,986 --> 01:06:10,919
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI GROANS)</font></b>

915
01:06:10,921 --> 01:06:12,790
