who crosses the horizon.

944
01:08:29,259 --> 01:08:30,994
I'm a real sailor!

945
01:08:36,967 --> 01:08:38,936
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(WIND WHISTLING)</font></b>

946
01:08:46,910 --> 01:08:47,911
Whoa!

947
01:08:49,046 --> 01:08:50,678
