954
01:09:09,967 --> 01:09:11,335
I think so.

955
01:09:13,603 --> 01:09:15,105
It's remarkable, right?

956
01:09:23,412 --> 01:09:25,349
Should we be worried?

957
01:09:28,352 --> 01:09:30,272
Hey, take the wheel,
I've just got to check this.

958
01:09:34,258 --> 01:09:35,656
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(RADIO BEEPS)</font></b>

959
01:09:35,658 --> 01:09:36,892
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#808080">MAN:</font></b> <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(ON RADIO)</font></b> <i>A warning
