960
01:09:36,894 --> 01:09:38,525
<i>High winds
and expected rainfall</i>

961
01:09:38,527 --> 01:09:40,594
<i>are now changed to
a tropical depression</i>

962
01:09:40,596 --> 01:09:41,997
<i>forming off Central America,</i>

963
01:09:41,999 --> 01:09:44,065
<i>and is now
classified as a Class 4.</i>

964
01:09:44,067 --> 01:09:46,700
<i>It's moving quickly
and increasing in strength,</i>

965
01:09:46,702 --> 01:09:49,770
<i>currently at 12 degrees north
and 107 degrees</i>

966
01:09:49,772 --> 01:09:51,239
<i>and moving west at 12 knots.</i>

967
01:09:51,241 --> 01:09:53,008
Babe, that's not good...

968
01:09:53,010 --> 01:09:55,776
<i>And a repeat, for those of you
just tuning in.</i>

969
01:09:55,778 --> 01:09:57,981
- Babe?
- Just one sec, please.

970
01:10:00,384 --> 01:10:04,518
Right, so we're at 11 north
and 123 west.

971
01:10:04,520 --> 01:10:06,288
That's well over
1,000 miles away

972
01:10:06,290 --> 01:10:07,888
