<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font></b>

1003
01:12:36,440 --> 01:12:37,640
Hey, babe.

1004
01:12:39,242 --> 01:12:40,542
Oh, my God.

1005
01:12:40,544 --> 01:12:42,845
