1012
01:13:15,412 --> 01:13:17,180
Let the sheet off now!

1013
01:13:18,181 --> 01:13:19,182
Okay.

1014
01:13:22,319 --> 01:13:23,953
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(TAMI PANTING)</font></b>

1015
01:13:40,137 --> 01:13:41,871
<b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(RICHARD GRUNTING)</font></b>

1016
01:13:43,473 --> 01:13:44,907
