feel like it disappears?

1025
01:14:20,109 --> 01:14:22,379
- Do you see?
- <b><font face="Rockwell" color="#D900D9">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font></b>

1026
01:14:27,384 --> 01:14:28,884
When I was little,

1027
01:14:30,019 --> 01:14:34,222
