1033
01:14:46,336 --> 01:14:49,972
He would take me surfing
and get me ice cream and...

1034
01:14:55,278 --> 01:14:57,711
The next morning,
he would always be gone.

1035
01:14:57,713 --> 01:14:58,812
We never knew
where he was going,

1036
01:14:58,814 --> 01:15:00,417
